description: RU a new? Have you heard about Douglass, historically known as the women's college at Rutgers? RU looking for a supportive community that will help you hit the ground running and get the most of your time here? Come check out Douglass where we focus on women's leadership by providing special opportunities for you to build your skills and surround yourself with students and staff who are passionate about social justice and centering women's lived experiences.  Meet new and current Douglass students and staff and hear about the opportunities and experiences that will enhance your college journey. From social events like International Women's Day to internship and research opportunities, Douglass enhances all majors and helps you build your resume and connections. Don't miss food and Douglass swag!!
